-- At Least Eight Killed, Many Injured in Pakistan Bomb Attack in Hyderabad
-- Farhan Sharif
-- 2010-06-28T07:30:35Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-28/at-least-eight-killed-many-injured-in-pakistan-bomb-attack-in-hyderabad.html

          
          
             At least eight people were killed
and 40 were injured in a bomb explosion in Pakistan’s southern
city of Hyderabad, Baboo Khan, a spokesman for the Edhi rescue
service, said by telephone.  
 “Many of the injured are in a serious condition,” said
Khan.   
